# Environment Configuration Files

## Frontend Environment Files

Create the following environment files in the Frontend directory:

### .env.development
```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

### .env.production
```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-production-url.com/api
```

### .env.staging
```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-staging-url.com/api
```

These files allow you to configure different API endpoints for different environments without modifying the source code.